            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>ShelfLife is a web application designed to reduce food waste by tracking expiration dates and suggesting recipes based on your inventory.</p>

            <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">The Problem</h2>
            <p>Every year, approximately 1.3 billion tonnes of food is wasted globally. This not only represents economic losses but also contributes significantly to greenhouse gas emissions and resource depletion.</p>

            <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Our Solution</h2>
            <p>ShelfLife helps you:</p>
            <ul style="margin-left: 2rem; margin-top: 0.5rem;">
                <li>Keep track of your food items and their expiry dates</li>
                <li>Get notifications when food is about to expire</li>
                <li>Find recipes that use ingredients you already have</li>
                <li>Reduce your food waste and save money</li>
            </ul>
